工厂，有些工厂里要用的东西也放在家里。第二，父亲很邋遢，随地吐痰，油瓶子倒了也不扶的人。母亲，囤积症，家具位置 20 年不变，坏了的笔、衣服的标签、不知来处的纽扣，家里这些东西堆积得很多。对了，爷爷奶奶和我们住在一起，老人家，什么东西都舍不得扔，不过，比我妈好点。 我现在没在家里住了，每次回家都感觉特别乱，特别难受。 我的问题是，有没有跟我一样住在一个脏乱差的地方住十几年的？什么感受？ 还有，如何让家人舍得扔呢？如何大刀阔斧花少钱让家里干净点呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-950125965beb230e0fce599542c96b13_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "382 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/47639633"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8oiZk9uJpuMREAMaCDExMjcwOTQzIO/Wn7sFMAY4iQdACnIINDc2Mzk2MzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1613469935.923626", "card_id": "Q_444533416", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 152}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待袁姗姗就「打呼噜」事件向张小斐道歉？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "《你好李焕英》热映。主演张小斐之前和袁姗姗参加综艺时的争议被拉了出来，袁姗姗刚刚发文向张小斐道歉称自己确实不太会讲话，但没有恶意。 ​"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a5ae3b6e8c689695be0d7029600a14d3_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "356 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444533416"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8oiZk9uJpuMREAMaCDYxMDYzODY4IJuzqIEGMAo4vgNAC3IJNDQ0NTMzNDE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1613469935.9240339", "card_id": "Q_277106464", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 222}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当今中国为什么不应该降低物理基础教育的难度？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当今中国应不应该降低数学基础教育的难度？ 相似问题，希望能回答下目前物理基础教育的问题。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-64bfc5b604006bf33a9a1d947bf4b28f_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "338 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/277106464"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8oiZk9uJpuMREAMaCDIzODU0ODA5IJ+25NcFMB04hwVADHIJMjc3MTA2NDY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9